ff and the patients you serve every day.With the Pharmacy Clinical Coordinators Handbook you can now develop the vision and strategy you need to succeed in this essential and demanding position.', DEFAULT, '56.8', '350', '2016-01-01', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=W3j0CwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Pharmacy Clinical Coordinator''s Handbook')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
