aims to prevent driver distraction from escalating into an even more significant problem.', DEFAULT, '127.96', '672', '2008-10-15', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=o7--7AS38tYC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Driver Distraction')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
