r of The Devil''s Casino comes an expos??? on the real estate elite that you''ll hardly believe.', DEFAULT, '15.99', '256', '2014-10-06', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=cVG_BAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'The Liar''s Ball')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
