n-Impaired Patient. The user-friendly layout now features more tables, boxes, and illustrations to speed you to important information. A new full-color design offers a wealth of vivid illustrations that clearly depict important procedures, concepts, and techniques.', DEFAULT, DEFAULT, '510', '2007', '4', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=uEmQKPAOwccC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Primary Care Optometry')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
