udy the statistical research associated with robust statistics.', DEFAULT, '95.99', '380', '2011-09-20', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=j1OhquR_j88C&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Robust Statistics')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
