sting, standard definition television in these countries continues to follow the NTSC standard in terms of frame rate and number of lines of resolution. In the United States a small number of...', DEFAULT, DEFAULT, '54', '2013-09', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=BsY5ngEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'Video Formats')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
