g and Public Health, Public Administration, Anthropology, Sociology, and Political Science.', DEFAULT, DEFAULT, '219', '2009', '8', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=FzawIAdilHkC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Case Study Research')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
