er plants, engines, and other applications.', DEFAULT, DEFAULT, '792', '2013-03-15', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Pxes4hlDmkIC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Oxygen-Enhanced Combustion, Second Edition')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
